"    - `Server Connection`__\n"
"    - Tryton Server Password: The password given in the Tryton server\n"
"      configuration.\n"
"    - File to Restore: Show filename and path.\n"
"    - New Database Name: Enter a new name for the database to be restored\n"
"    - Actions:"
